      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TATTOOED BEAST (2) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 520m behind Garritty (30.44) in a Grade 5. Was a winner the start prior. Has ability and is a key runner. SUNSET CALIGULA (6) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in seven starts, including six wins. Placed last time (27.74) at Mandurah in a Grade 4/5, finishing second and beaten 2.5 lengths. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. OOSTHUIZEN (1) skirted wide from an outside draw last start and found the front, leading throughout to win (30.20) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 520m. Likely to be in the finish. UNCHECKED (3) can fill a top-three spot.",
